&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Hearing is a &lt;strong>natural phenomenon&lt;/strong> to normal ears. &lt;br>
Listening is a &lt;strong>conscious phenomenon&lt;/strong> from a willing mind. &lt;br>
It is possible that with a normal ear I can hear but not listen. &lt;br>
And it is also possible that with a deaf ear I may not hear but listen.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>